{"ts":"2026-06-27T08:27:51.512Z","type":"agent_event","event":{"type":"content_start","contentType":"reasoning","reasoning":"**Visualizing Access Block Diagram**\n\nI am now designing the interactive \"Enclave Clearance Diagram\" for the \"Clearance Insufficient\" screen within `PreviewRouteGuard.tsx`. My idea is a vertical stack representing clearance levels, from I to V. Each level, color-coded and labeled (Auditor to Superuser), will be a node on the stack. The current role is highlighted, and the target section's required level is displayed, along with a firewall visual.\n\n\n","redacted":false}}
